0075|- [HelpText]
0076|*Plotting on the screen:
0078|SUse GPLOT (instead of PLOT) as the operation word. When a GPLOT
S   |     77777
0079|*operation is activated, the plot will be generated in its own window
0080|*and it is also saved as an enhanced metafile (.EMF).
0082|*The number, sizes and locations of simultaneous graphics windows
0083|*are selected by a GPLOT /LAYOUT command.
0084|*For example, if the number of permitted graphics windows is 3,
0085|*the 4th graph will close window #1, 5th graph will close window #2, etc.
0087|*All graphics windows of SURVO MM can be freely moved, resized, minimized,
0088|*maximized, and deleted by using the mouse.
0090|*The Survo device driver defining the various control words
0091|*to be used in the GPLOT operation is selected by the keyword
